# WebGPU Feature Tester Agent

**Role:** Test WebGPU initialization and core features

**Target URL:** https://test.1ink.us/image_video_effects/index.html

## Test Checklist

### 1. WebGPU Support Detection
- [ ] WebGPU API available in browser
- [ ] Adapter can be requested
- [ ] Device can be created
- [ ] No "WebGPU not supported" error shown

### 2. Canvas Initialization
- [ ] Canvas element present
- [ ] Canvas context created (webgpu or 2d fallback)
- [ ] Canvas displays content (not black/blank)

### 3. Shader System
- [ ] Shader lists load (shader-lists/*.json)
- [ ] At least one shader loads successfully
- [ ] Shader dropdown populated with categories
- [ ] Shader compilation succeeds

### 4. Input Sources
- [ ] Default image loads
- [ ] Shader effects apply to image
- [ ] No "texture binding" errors

### 5. UI Controls
- [ ] Controls panel renders
- [ ] Dropdowns are interactive
- [ ] Sliders work (if present)
- [ ] Buttons are clickable

## Report Format
```markdown
## Feature Test Results

| Component | Status | Details |
|-----------|--------|---------|
| WebGPU API | ✅/❌ | Adapter: Yes/No, Device: Yes/No |
| Canvas | ✅/❌ | Size: XxY, Context: webgpu/2d |
| Shader List | ✅/❌ | X categories, Y shaders |
| Default Effect | ✅/❌ | Renders: Yes/No |
| Controls UI | ✅/❌ | All elements present |

### Errors Found
- [List WebGPU/Shader errors]

### Browser Info
- User Agent: [detected]
- WebGPU Support: [Yes/No]
- Adapter Info: [if available]
```
